or you want to mourn your wife.

55
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:59,678
Now let's eat, I'm starved.

56
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:03,918
In the name of the Father,
the Son and the Holy Ghost.

57
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:06,358
Lord, bless this food.

58
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,838
Our Father...

59
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:11,920
Who art in heaven,
